Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.20,0:01:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但会是皆大欢喜的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.99,0:01:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}好人会如愿以偿
