Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.30,0:03:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}第一百章
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:31.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我们还有一个月时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.88,0:03:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们该做些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.55,0:03:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好生活
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:36.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你需要把书写完  -没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我负责婚礼筹备工作
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.93,0:03:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我感觉时间过得太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实很快  朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.52,0:03:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:54.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三周半之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.36,0:03:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的书终于写完了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的编辑喜欢新的结局  -你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我大概喜欢百分98.5吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我已经接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.04,0:04:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永远也不会完全满意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太焦虑了  关键问题试试
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.17,0:04:09.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经打了"完结"  准备暑假发行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.76,0:04:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.80,0:04:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着我们应该吃次正餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.09,0:04:16.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26美元一位  不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.51,0:04:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我外婆的教堂朋友们能找到方法去吃自助餐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.39,0:04:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们以前干过  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.27,0:04:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我准备好谈谈婚礼的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.60,0:04:23.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.31,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊  我真是喜欢看你弄清单
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真让人兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.48,0:04:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.19,0:04:29.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经给婚庆公司订金了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.32,0:04:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕和DJ都确定了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.94,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我给供应商和客人都发邮件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提醒他们马拉松在这周末
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.32,0:04:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以交通状况会不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.66,0:04:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你巧舌如簧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.95,0:04:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳娜确认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.37,0:04:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼服在运输途中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.79,0:04:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续说点开放性问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:46.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你来说点开放性问题吧  -我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.42,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼前一天我们分开睡还是一起睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.63,0:04:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-一起  肯定的  -同意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经宣誓了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:53.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有史以来我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.22,0:04:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,按时完成写作任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.68,0:04:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我第一次没有按时完成
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.55,0:04:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我的书
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.97,0:04:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.10,0:05:00.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有担心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.93,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们还需要再做一件事情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.89,0:05:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,练习舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甜蜜的过分了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜欢座位卡上都是心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.12,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是三年级小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.99,0:05:21.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定你不想邀请
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.79,0:05:23.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更多人加入彩排晚餐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:26.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简不需要动她书的钱  我请客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.87,0:05:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们想弄小点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.34,0:05:31.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果你想弄大一号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那恰恰不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.71,0:05:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很高兴能够与玛贝拉酒店永远在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}#佩特拉·玛贝拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.63,0:05:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}#永远热情好客
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在谈谈时间安排吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.26,0:05:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸡尾酒会是5点到6点  然后是晚宴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.14,0:05:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚宴时  我们开始敬酒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.35,0:05:44.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.06,0:05:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我也会敬酒  -是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  而且还会很有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但佩特拉并不有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:54.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道  但是她很激动  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.32,0:05:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-她停顿的时候笑一笑吧  -我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.86,0:05:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非她当众开除某人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.49,0:05:59.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,礼服合身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.49,0:06:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完美  琳娜选的很准
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.24,0:06:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.41,0:06:03.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我等不及想看你穿礼服了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:06.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱你  家里见
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.08,0:06:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.25,0:06:09.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到了你的邮件  我们愿意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.58,0:06:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你给我们的灵魂证婚  不过我们认为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.50,0:06:14.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这更像是婚礼之后私下的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.09,0:06:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  但是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实希望和你谈点别的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不是好事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.22,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  什么事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到了拉斐尔的生父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.93,0:06:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  看来最后的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.89,0:06:28.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终还是会被揭晓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.91,0:06:35.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所想象的  或者是我想象的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.67,0:06:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,故事可以有很多种结局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.13,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找到拉斐尔的父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.67,0:06:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结局可能是戏剧性的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是黑社会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.17,0:06:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也可能令人震惊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.97,0:06:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,萝丝不是他的母亲  对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.64,0:06:46.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者看似平凡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.18,0:06:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的父母曾经是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:50.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.85,0:06:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.14,0:06:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他们去世了  -当然  这是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.27,0:06:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一种完全不同的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.36,0:06:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我能找到的关于他们的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.66,0:07:06.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该由你来告诉拉斐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.41,0:07:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我给你说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:17.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你得带一件更暖的外套  希尔玛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:19.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷了我会去买的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,纽约有地方逛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.46,0:07:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.26,0:07:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}确保我联系你时你不冷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我可听不出区别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.56,0:07:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}好呀宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特奥在哪儿  我得回家和拉斐尔谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.23,0:07:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在楼上  他说他在给我准备一个大惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.61,0:07:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特奥  你干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拆了你的包裹  这样你就不用搬家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来简的儿子也不喜欢离别
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.95,0:07:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特奥  亲爱的  外婆还是得搬家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.04,0:07:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道的  因为外公的事业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.54,0:07:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以外公不得不离开
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.96,0:08:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但外婆可以和我们呆在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.71,0:08:03.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不  我不能  亲爱的  -是的  你可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:04.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只是不想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:06.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不是这样的  -你要是想的话当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:07.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  马特奥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们说好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吗  我们每晚都会视频通话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.35,0:08:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:18.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你的感受  伙计
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.15,0:08:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.98,0:08:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你们怎么才来  -我们有点小问题
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们好多了  对吧笑眯眯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我能和你们一起睡在床上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不公平  如果他可以  那么我们也要一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是  别大吵大闹的  马特奥  -说梦话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.66,0:08:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不吵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.00,0:08:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是很吵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.21,0:08:39.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的决定是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-听你们的  -太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:44.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚睡觉的时候别这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.13,0:08:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.97,0:08:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家人之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.51,0:08:51.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好那就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴里  你是个出色的经纪人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.02,0:08:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了吸引注意力  电视台在秋季播出前
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:06.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发布了《这是火星》的线上试播集
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.15,0:09:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢相信它终于在美国开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.03,0:09:11.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人们正在观看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.41,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得会受欢迎吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.87,0:09:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希尔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.50,0:09:18.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.46,0:09:20.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,#火星这个标签火起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美国果然是爱我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像大家爱的是宇航局
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.80,0:09:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又有一辆火星车在火星着陆了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:33.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你打包  换个话题
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这令人很激动  不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来可期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.40,0:09:45.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路易莎找到我父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.19,0:09:48.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  但我不知道除了直说以外
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能怎么告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.03,0:09:52.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们死于车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.37,0:09:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们住在意大利
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.37,0:10:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们拥有一家面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就是这样  -面包店
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.46,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太平凡无奇了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:10.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜我大概是在期待一些
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.84,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂剧的情节
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.47,0:10:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更大的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.72,0:10:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更疯狂的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被我说中了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:19.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道现在是得知这件事的最差时机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟马上就要举办婚礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.73,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.52,0:10:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事实上  现在是最佳时机
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.19,0:10:29.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是在几个月前  我可能会很绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我现在所能想到的全部就是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拥有多少东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确实被家人环绕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.95,0:10:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我除了感激之外还能有何感受呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虚晃一枪  但毕竟箭在弦上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.25,0:10:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不得不发啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我迫不及待地想嫁给你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.09,0:10:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就带我们来到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  走快点
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.18,0:10:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑娘们  回去那边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.60,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马特奥  你怎么脱了裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.35,0:11:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好  只是彩排而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.68,0:11:03.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}为什么没人把这当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这已经是第三次走过场了  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.85,0:11:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.19,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}罗格里奥的妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.40,0:11:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.52,0:11:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好啊  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.19,0:11:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过来  我的帅小伙儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.65,0:11:16.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.91,0:11:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要在婚礼上朗诵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你可要好好练习声音的投射
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:23.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让位置不好的观众也能听到你的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:25.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:29.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}行了  我们结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.88,0:11:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  你写誓词了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.34,0:11:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就写
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.80,0:11:40.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出版社这周要印刷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我那本书的试阅本
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.06,0:11:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送去给作家们评论
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.98,0:11:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但等等  这还不是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其中一位作家是伊莎贝尔·阿连德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}著名女作家  代表作《幽灵之家》  被誉为"穿裙子的加西亚·马尔克斯"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.11,0:11:52.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莎贝尔·阿连德也许会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写一段我书背后的简介
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳娜  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  抱歉  我挺好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伊莎贝拉什么的  耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.29,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  我本来打算等到婚礼结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再告诉你的  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我怀孕啦  -天哪  恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.09,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是哪个姐妹给你的卵子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很明显是更好看的那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.72,0:12:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-亚历克西斯吗  -是杰姬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.60,0:12:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就这意思  我一直搞混她俩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.93,0:12:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真为你感到高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.98,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有你这个超幸运的小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.27,0:12:30.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  够了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我该滔滔不绝地发表一些关于你的感言了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.15,0:12:36.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准确来说  她还真这么做了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都觉得我和四个姐姐一起长大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但事实上  我有五个姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.12,0:12:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只喜欢其中一个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.21,0:12:49.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  你对我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意味着一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我在这个世界上最佩服的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.05,0:12:58.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我长大后想成为你这样的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:05.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是  在晚年
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:07.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为简的父亲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.94,0:13:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这辈子最大的乐趣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.19,0:13:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这话是真的  并且
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天  我也很开心我会有个儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  拉斐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.62,0:13:28.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能叫我一声爸爸  我将不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:37.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.51,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.01,0:13:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会搞明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.22,0:13:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  今晚大家也哭哭啼啼这么久了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:51.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我觉得也是时候来一点欢笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都知道简很着迷于婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她上班时总是和番茄酱结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔  他一直都...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.99,0:14:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的衬衫太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且他的裤子...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.68,0:14:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系  佩特拉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.96,0:14:11.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不必要说的很搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是为了不像这样激动才写了这些笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.06,0:14:16.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得好像这样没效果
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.59,0:14:20.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是太喜欢你们两个了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的爱情正是我所渴望的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.48,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还在祝你们一切幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种感觉真是太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我通常不会祝别人幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:35.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我爱你  -我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.20,0:14:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢各位
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想说一段祝酒词
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  很久以前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我经历了一段艰难的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.25,0:15:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我不小心让你受孕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:06.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我想趁此时机说...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简单地说  那天晚上  充满了爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.15,0:15:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,实际上  简突然意识到了一些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.62,0:15:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又有那种表情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.99,0:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你想去写作吗  -很快就好  可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-当然  去吧  -好的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.92,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来你为爱哽咽了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:46.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托  维兰纽瓦的事就是会让人们哭的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们就是为此而打造的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.70,0:15:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  我很好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.16,0:15:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简跑到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:54.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她在这
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.20,0:15:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来有人被这些祝酒词激发了灵感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.08,0:16:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  我不会告诉别人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的作家妻子  抄袭了她自己的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是在写我的结婚誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是突然想到了该怎么写书的结尾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:13.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我就能达到100%了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.38,0:16:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后发给我的编辑  看她能不能及时将文件
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送去打印店  然后再拿给伊莎贝尔·阿连德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.66,0:16:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来打算今晚晚点再写我的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:24.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的  人们常说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.91,0:16:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡着截止时间交的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.14,0:16:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是最棒的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:32.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们应该回去了  要上甜点了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.93,0:16:35.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我肯定吃了太多蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.53,0:16:38.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很难过  我能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.53,0:16:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是让拉斐尔为难了  但也是出于好心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.05,0:16:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格里奥  不是这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.83,0:16:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要给你说件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.54,0:16:53.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想我不会搬去纽约
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.35,0:17:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思  你不能搬去纽约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.07,0:17:05.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是不想离开我的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.19,0:17:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我一直在试着将这种感觉放到一边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.15,0:17:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来支持你  但是我真的认为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我来说  这不是正确的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.90,0:17:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的护校学习
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.89,0:17:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才刚刚顺利开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的生活终于回到了正轨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.18,0:17:18.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必须得走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.18,0:17:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我签了一份合同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:25.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:27.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们能经常来往
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.80,0:17:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这一年
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.50,0:17:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工作日我会住在这
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.11,0:17:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了周末  我们会去轮流看望彼此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,考虑一下吧  反正你的时间很长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:39.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不用在周中你拍戏的时候来看你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.14,0:17:45.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样通勤会让你幸福吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.13,0:17:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想会的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.52,0:17:49.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.02,0:17:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  罗格里奥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我写完了我的婚礼誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:07.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前那事我很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不  是我反应过度了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.03,0:18:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的书非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才非常重要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.23,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我并不担心该怎么写我的誓言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.06,0:18:19.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很清楚我想说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能每天和你在一起都是多么的幸运
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非常期待我们的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我对我们的未来感到非常兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.57,0:18:34.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这不像是我从小到大所看的肥皂剧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:37.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼并不是结束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.44,0:18:40.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的故事才刚刚开始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别再提了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得我有点脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚你告诉我  我的生父母去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这并没有让我感到慌乱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.97,0:18:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.45,0:18:59.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这对一个人来讲真的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为我等不及未来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.31,0:19:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想跳过这个时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就别等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:09.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们直接去度蜜月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  最终我们要大肆挥霍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.93,0:19:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我们从来没去度过假
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在航班还有酒店预定上有一百万个积分
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.23,0:19:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们几乎不用花钱
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.60,0:19:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该不用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我加入
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.88,0:19:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,转身回了家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.45,0:19:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.00,0:19:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外婆叫我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.22,0:19:46.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不打算走是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:51.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我考虑过了  这不是我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是说  我不该颠倒我的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.24,0:19:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不是二十世纪五十年代了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:56.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直想上卫校
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.99,0:19:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说你想去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.09,0:20:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我改变主意了  我想待在这
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.42,0:20:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为马特奥把你吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是个孩子  妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.10,0:20:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.47,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我不想我就不用去  我不想去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.81,0:20:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想待在这见证一些事  比如你的书出版了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.79,0:20:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有晚餐  生日聚会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.50,0:20:15.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你被吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.56,0:20:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太愚蠢了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我四十六岁了  我这一辈子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.98,0:20:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都生活在你身边  妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这辈子也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.03,0:20:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会想起我们的简并不喜欢结局
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.86,0:20:36.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在呢  就这么结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.12,0:20:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她从她妈妈身上遗传的品质
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}不
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}它会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}那才是可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.06,0:20:48.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但如果我能来到这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.54,0:20:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}重新再来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你肯定会在纽约做同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.29,0:20:59.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}被吓到也没关系  希尔玛拉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.26,0:21:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.72,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}让恐惧再影响到我们的生活可就不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.58,0:21:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会和我一起去纽约吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.73,0:21:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天哪  我太荣幸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太爱你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.12,0:21:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.12,0:21:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在这做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.64,0:21:28.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是过来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你这个  为了明天的婚礼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.03,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是条  项链
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.23,0:21:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没打算戴什么首饰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.19,0:21:39.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是新娘套索
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.78,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一条墨西哥式婚礼念珠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.54,0:21:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼的时候  亲友们把它绕到新郎新娘身上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.56,0:21:47.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是结合的象征
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.04,0:21:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲把它给我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.29,0:21:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在  我想把它传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:21:57.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时  我想道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.10,0:21:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让你因为叫我爸爸这些事而感到为难
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.89,0:22:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们现在是在私下里  所以
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.95,0:22:07.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你想试试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.40,0:22:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.96,0:22:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是什么张嘴就来的事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.70,0:22:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你知道我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.98,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}九百六十万粉丝  五万五千三百八十二人正在关注
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道  我火了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.75,0:22:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}一千二百七十万粉丝  五万五千三百八十二人正在关注
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.73,0:22:26.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线上有事发生  但是
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.92,0:22:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  这时他才意识到...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.54,0:22:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.76,0:22:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的粉丝量在暴涨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.15,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经双倍
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.13,0:22:37.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  变成三倍了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.64,0:22:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说人们肯定在看《这是火星》试播集
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.27,0:22:45.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许就是现在了  拉斐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能在美国走红了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.11,0:22:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.59,0:22:56.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过这事我们暂且保密
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.87,0:22:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不想抢了简的风头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:00.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她明天就要结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:02.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.38,0:23:03.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.98,0:23:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们共度的最后一晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.99,0:23:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:08.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}行了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.22,0:23:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你们俩别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.80,0:23:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}明天可是简的大喜之日
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.68,0:23:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}该睡觉咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:18.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.37,0:23:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁忘记关灯了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.99,0:23:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天可是我大喜的日子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.42,0:23:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要搬走了  心里难过着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.65,0:23:40.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.56,0:23:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我来关
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:44.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱你哟  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.30,0:24:01.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}这是我在你受洗那天读的讲稿
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.50,0:24:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你可以在简的受洗仪式上读
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.62,0:24:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}画出十字
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.63,0:24:28.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我深深感受到了屋里充满的关爱与支持
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.52,0:24:48.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  曾经
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.22,0:24:51.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也有这样的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.78,0:25:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可惜  那一刻已经过去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.26,0:25:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.20,0:25:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我的编辑
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.97,0:25:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不重要
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.74,0:25:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我眼里...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.10,0:26:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有他
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.85,0:26:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  我的新郎
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.53,0:26:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的准新娘  新婚快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.15,0:26:08.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根据预定计划
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.88,0:26:10.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发型师和化妆师应该就快...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.42,0:26:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们正好来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.84,0:26:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.94,0:26:14.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的编辑及时收到你的更改内容了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.66,0:26:17.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有  不过这不重要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.07,0:26:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会在正式印刷时换过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.09,0:26:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可伊莎贝尔·阿连德呢  她不肯看你的结局
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.20,0:26:23.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肯定能做些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就只能亲手把U盘
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.88,0:26:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,送到印刷厂了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.52,0:26:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当然不会在新婚之日去送
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.00,0:26:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.08,0:26:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不打算今天跑去经历什么奇遇
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.29,0:26:34.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们祭坛上见
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.18,0:26:35.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.09,0:26:36.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.28,0:26:42.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她或许没这打算
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.91,0:26:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可看起来他有
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.33,0:26:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗  有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.14,0:26:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}蒂莫西与汤普森出版社
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.79,0:26:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.12,0:27:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,停止出版
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.01,0:27:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们都这样说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.13,0:27:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二十年代才这么说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.10,0:27:05.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.71,0:27:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想请您帮个大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.91,0:27:13.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三十分钟后
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.63,0:27:13.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是多谢了  老兄
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.03,0:27:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你帮了我大忙了  -不客气
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.08,0:27:15.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-祝你好运  兄弟  -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.68,0:27:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.21,0:27:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.33,0:27:41.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.00,0:27:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来简得花大钱赔那道门了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.10,0:27:56.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗨  准老公
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.34,0:27:58.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  我进展顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.16,0:28:01.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的计划可能要有所改变
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.06,0:28:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被抓了  得有人把我保释出来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.89,0:28:11.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到家庭故事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.85,0:28:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个故事将经常被谈起
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.49,0:28:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他开车冲过了那道门
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.12,0:28:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后被抓了  我得去把他保出来
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.23,0:28:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可老妈开走了车去接乔治了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.21,0:28:20.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再叫辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.53,0:28:22.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  简  我去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.55,0:28:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-今天是你的婚礼  -所以必须我去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.74,0:28:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉弗真是太浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.22,0:28:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,必须是我去接他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.18,0:28:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.16,0:28:31.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还能出什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.95,0:28:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}十分种路程
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.68,0:28:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:41.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.43,0:28:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,软件上说你离我十分种路程远
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.27,0:28:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这都过去二十分钟了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.39,0:28:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为马拉松比赛  我过不去
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.43,0:28:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能在普利茅斯街上车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.43,0:28:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离你只有几个街区远
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.19,0:28:49.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.68,0:28:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就过去
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.43,0:29:03.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.54,0:29:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,借过一下
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.99,0:29:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头发真好看
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.87,0:29:06.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.96,0:29:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.72,0:29:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.52,0:29:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.82,0:29:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-别停下  -谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.92,0:29:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}司机已取消行程
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.57,0:29:19.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,菲利普
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.06,0:29:22.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然之间
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.81,0:29:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知是巧合还是一场巨大的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.21,0:29:33.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车吧  简
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.01,0:29:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}还有十五站
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:44.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  有没有什么办法
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.74,0:29:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能直接绕路
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.61,0:29:46.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.05,0:29:48.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.20,0:29:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她还不知道什么是公交车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.05,0:29:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我今天结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.30,0:29:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和我的未婚夫经历了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.89,0:29:55.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,意外人工授精  绑架  邪恶双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.97,0:29:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起死回生的丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.16,0:29:58.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们最后的障碍了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.16,0:30:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你  能帮帮我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.86,0:30:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.85,0:30:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我愿意用五千块租下整辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.68,0:30:09.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来简终于决定怎么挥霍这笔钱了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.95,0:30:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.92,0:30:13.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要给我们多少钱
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.13,0:30:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每人五十
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.42,0:30:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一百
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.18,0:30:19.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还有事要做  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.21,0:30:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去银行  干洗店
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.86,0:30:22.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-美甲店  -二百
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.24,0:30:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能再多了  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.21,0:30:24.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,婚礼56分钟后就开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.79,0:30:30.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.38,0:30:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.84,0:30:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去警察局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.40,0:30:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.83,0:30:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.06,0:30:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在哪儿  我们等着你们呢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.47,0:30:55.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就过去  我接到新郎了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.88,0:30:57.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我发短信告诉你上车的地点
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.61,0:30:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你开什么车  够大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.44,0:31:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对够大
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.64,0:31:08.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让一让
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.82,0:31:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让简·格洛瑞娜·维兰纽瓦的婚礼团过去
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.05,0:31:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.59,0:31:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保护婚纱
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.27,0:31:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们  就在这时
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.11,0:31:21.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是罗格里奥·维嘉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.52,0:31:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚播的那部《这是火星》
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.62,0:31:23.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里面的那个人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.77,0:31:26.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你很搞笑
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.04,0:31:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.97,0:31:30.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格里奥·维嘉  美国影星
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.17,0:31:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很快就是了  朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.34,0:31:35.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提前尝鲜一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.23,0:31:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来[转型]
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.05,0:31:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.79,0:31:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.25,0:31:46.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.23,0:31:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  我们到了  你们在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.41,0:31:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:31:51.41,0:31:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们走
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.30,0:31:57.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夫人  你站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.23,0:31:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先生  能站在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.07,0:32:00.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也别看  转过去
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.51,0:32:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}站进来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.88,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但把裙子提起来
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.59,0:32:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红灯停车了  把眼线笔给我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.25,0:32:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们在后面怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.36,0:32:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不要看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.28,0:32:12.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你疯了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.20,0:32:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.84,0:32:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.63,0:32:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}离婚礼还有0分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.94,0:32:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下我们真迟到了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.24,0:32:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别紧张  你们没到  他们不会开始的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.13,0:32:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以前我当新郎的时候也紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.88,0:32:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是三次  但谁记着这种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.53,0:32:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们会完婚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.28,0:32:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会幸福美满地在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.09,0:32:39.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然不总是美满
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.00,0:32:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时  会遇到不顺的事
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.32,0:32:45.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们会吵架  会急得跺脚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.47,0:32:47.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少我会急得跺脚
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.92,0:32:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你们会熬过困境
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.02,0:32:52.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你们会有很多快乐的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.79,0:32:54.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这倒是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.96,0:32:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很多快乐的时光
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.25,0:32:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.19,0:33:00.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗格里奥很好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.58,0:33:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呼气
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.67,0:33:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吸气
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.29,0:33:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.37,0:33:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都放轻松
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.93,0:33:10.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}婚礼已过六分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.37,0:33:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新郎新娘随时会到
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.91,0:33:13.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我有一些笑话
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.26,0:33:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在彩排晚宴上没机会说
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.83,0:33:16.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁现在想听听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.25,0:33:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在不想  以后也不想
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.71,0:33:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.50,0:33:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.63,0:33:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐  我没准备好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.85,0:33:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是新娘简
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.49,0:33:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她真美
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.53,0:33:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么来了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.43,0:33:38.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔打电话给我
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.73,0:33:39.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.37,0:33:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我说你对我还有感觉 
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:44.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他苦口婆心地和我说人生苦短
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.43,0:33:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道很老土
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.56,0:33:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我妈刚过世
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.16,0:33:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我最近一直在想你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.20,0:33:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说实话  我一直爱着你
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.64,0:33:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.25,0:34:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也爱你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.06,0:34:10.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲过世我感到很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.32,0:34:11.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.97,0:34:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你母亲的事我也很难过
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.63,0:34:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别担心  她也走了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.67,0:34:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  我来告诉大家她去了哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.03,0:34:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}西伯利亚某地
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.17,0:34:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}彼得
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}妈妈来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.79,0:34:35.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.14,0:34:38.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三胞胎之一
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.47,0:34:38.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只能说是从肥皂剧里抄来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.83,0:34:43.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们回到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.26,0:34:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了  我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.09,0:34:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.46,0:34:50.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你准备好结婚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.17,0:34:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:34:59.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.48,0:35:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我一直在告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂剧通常以婚礼收尾
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.35,0:35:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经历了一段漫长之旅后
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.14,0:35:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于开始自己的旅程了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:25.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.00,0:35:57.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,值得注意的是  在这美好的一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.67,0:35:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简的激动之情包括了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.63,0:36:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.73,0:36:04.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.25,0:36:08.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烤芝士三明治
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.67,0:36:10.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写作
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.28,0:36:15.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔·索拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.60,0:36:36.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢大家今天赏光出席
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.24,0:36:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先  我们精选了《爱是你我》的一段话
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.32,0:36:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱是你  爱是我
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.82,0:36:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我会随着你一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.45,0:36:56.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有你在旁  天空湛蓝
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.91,0:36:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犹如幸福加倍
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.57,0:37:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱很欢乐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.21,0:37:09.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无拘无束  爱能让人随心而动
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.91,0:37:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你念这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.87,0:37:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和曾祖木一起练习的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.43,0:37:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说我很适合做配音
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.58,0:37:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我声明  我是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.03,0:37:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我自己这么说可能不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来的话我要用西班牙语说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.11,0:37:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们中有人不懂西班牙语
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.48,0:37:30.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在手册中有翻译
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.47,0:37:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我们今天聚在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.04,0:37:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}见证我深爱的外孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.13,0:37:48.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}简·格洛瑞娜·维兰纽瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.02,0:37:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}嫁给拉斐尔·索拉诺
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.62,0:37:52.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我也非常爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.12,0:37:54.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}他唯一的缺点是
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.80,0:37:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}不是天主教徒  所以我必须在这个露天教堂之中作见证
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.02,0:38:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.02,0:38:03.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我很高兴我可以作见证
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.78,0:38:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}因为站在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.78,0:38:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}看着你们结合
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.44,0:38:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}会是我
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.61,0:38:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}余生珍视的时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.19,0:38:16.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我声明  这是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.96,0:38:19.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}伊莎贝尔·阿连德曾说过
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.40,0:38:24.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}"你是你人生故事的讲述者"
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.88,0:38:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}简和拉斐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.62,0:38:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你们让我知道  这句话很正确
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.54,0:38:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}因为你们一路走来  风雨波折  就像电视剧一样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.00,0:38:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}但不管怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.15,0:38:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你们为彼此而战
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.63,0:38:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}确信你们必将在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.08,0:38:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}现在你们终于如命中注定般在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.32,0:38:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我想请新娘的父母上来
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.21,0:39:01.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}进行一项墨西哥传统仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.65,0:39:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们把这个套在你们身上
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.34,0:39:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,象征着合一和承诺
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.59,0:39:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在你们之间
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.75,0:39:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永远紧密相连了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.12,0:39:19.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.36,0:39:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.26,0:39:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.26,0:39:35.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}现在你们可以交换结婚誓言了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.71,0:39:39.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.10,0:39:43.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.65,0:39:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.00,0:39:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你让...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.86,0:39:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你先说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.81,0:40:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔  我们第一次见面时
Dialogue: 0,0:40:00.67,0:40:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你告诉我要勇敢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.00,0:40:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.98,0:40:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.29,0:40:11.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.97,0:40:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许我们应该...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.92,0:40:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  没错  -抱歉  我们要
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.26,0:40:21.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-自己读一下  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.34,0:40:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友们
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.34,0:40:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们做到了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.88,0:40:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}现在还没到时间呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.88,0:40:37.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  抱歉  抱歉  外婆
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.38,0:40:40.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}那我快一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.38,0:40:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}戒指呢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.88,0:40:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,199.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}现在你们可以交换
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.68,0:40:53.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}象征着爱和忠诚的戒指了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.94,0:41:00.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉斐尔  请接受这枚象征着爱和忠诚的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.76,0:41:05.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.51,0:41:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-抱歉  -简
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.59,0:41:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.07,0:41:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请接受这枚象征着爱和忠诚的戒指
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.27,0:41:20.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.88,0:41:22.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}别亲了  再等三十秒
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.58,0:41:26.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}要不我直接说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.88,0:41:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}我宣布你们结为夫妻
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.38,0:41:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(192,219.274)}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs17\b1\bord0\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&\c&H67E3E8&}你可以亲吻新娘了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.28,0:41:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.88,0:41:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  女士们
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.11,0:41:49.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新郎  新郎  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.11,0:41:51.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-快进来  -来吧  亲爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.14,0:41:52.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-很好  -没错  来吧  马特奥
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.81,0:41:54.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就这样  佩特拉  你也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.56,0:41:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-来吧  来啊  路易莎  -路易莎
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.99,0:41:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  你好啊  宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.00,0:42:00.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等下  等下  接住了  给你
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.84,0:42:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.23,0:42:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-德斯  -天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.90,0:42:23.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要回到里面去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.86,0:42:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再坐一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.42,0:42:33.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有问过你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.30,0:42:34.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.79,0:42:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那本书的结局是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.27,0:42:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把这本书的故事  拍成了一部肥皂剧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.46,0:42:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁会想看这样的剧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.46,0:42:53.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}全剧终

